          <li>Your services are liable to be terminated without notice if you
            are found indulging in any kind of propaganda, political activity,
            misbehaviours, intimidation, violence, wilfully damaging any
            property belonging to company, its clients or other employees and
            not observing company laid down discipline within the premises.
          </li>
          <li>You shall submit a report of monthly performance (as per format
